This project is a rewrite of what was formerly known as "Open
Broadcaster Software", software originally designed for recording and
streaming live video content, efficiently.

This build requires the Chromium Embedded Framework (CEF) for browser
source support on x86_64.

32-bit (i586/i686) builds are supported but without browser source
support, as no 32-bit CEF binary is available for obs-studio 32.x.
Browser source support is automatically disabled on 32-bit systems.

Homepage: https://obsproject.com/
